{"tid":721800,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[知道條垃圾唔對路] 皇馬大平賣　C朗違約金減價8成","createTime":"2018-06-29T03:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T05:21:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0812910863e63661f4e74e15170262c38ff8c815","tid":721800,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"06月29日(五) 01:50\t<br />\n<br />\nC朗喺世界盃表現勇猛，帶領葡萄牙殺入16強，不過皇家馬德里似乎唔放在眼內，西班牙傳媒爆料，皇馬已經狠下決心買走C朗，準備喺明年1月將違約金由10億歐元(約90.9億港元)大幅減至1.2億歐元(約10.9億港元)，令稍有財力嘅球會都可以收購C朗，等同放棄呢位葡萄牙球星。<br />\n<br />\n其實C朗一直希望皇馬加人工，因為佢嘅年薪大幅落後於美斯同尼馬，但皇馬唔想為C朗破壞球隊薪酬結構，搞到冇偈傾，至於違約金大減方案，原因係C朗經理人<span style=\"color: red;\">接獲來自曼城、阿仙奴、車路士及AC米蘭報價</span>，各球會都願意支付大約1.2億歐元轉會費，因此皇馬亦開出呢個違約金價位。<br />\n<br />\n不過，只有兩間球會例外，分別係巴塞隆拿同巴黎聖日耳門，上述兩隊想收購C朗，就要畀足10億歐元！"},{"pid":"d609014bb0ebcd953c9992a228d83cea7ea114e1","tid":721800,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我買佢返來日日教我踢波"},{"pid":"61ea1f56124ab64a4a2ec58bbbc623379efbb9a5","tid":721800,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f91befea19b2ed3db350f27a86d9553e83aa4fd","tid":721800,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d609014bb0ebcd953c9992a228d83cea7ea114e1","tid":721800,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我買佢返來日日教我踢波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-Shn33hSzJd0/VTSUW7V6PeI/AAAAAAAAD1A/bCdOFClNNSM/w638-h358-no/EricSoC%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%BF%E5%BA%A6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2F-Shn33hSzJd0%2FVTSUW7V6PeI%2FAAAAAAAAD1A%2FbCdOFClNNSM%2Fw638-h358-no%2FEricSoC%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25BA%25A6.jpg&h=5fee614b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3633eb2cd86eebb8f9fe4d6e619934899cdba306","tid":721800,"uid":44698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"皇馬已經狠下決心買走C朗<br />\n<br />\n買賣都未識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係支那報？"},{"pid":"73c331dea5f34c7b757695ec3ea1642be80c4b92","tid":721800,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"Ac禁一年買黎雪？"},{"pid":"eb9400575478e6ee4d1d90d4db653efa25a00af1","tid":721800,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"Carpio (Marca Director): &quot;The clause of Cristiano is still one billion, according to the club&quot;"}]}